description:
In this episode of ANN In-Depth, Sam Neves talks with Fylvia Kline, manager of Vivid Faith, about the mission and the voluntary spirit that has been ingrained in Adventists since their inception.

Listen to the full episode to learn about what Vivid Faith is, its challenges, and how it has been involved in volunteer work among Adventists and entities.

https://youtu.be/l205S56cXJg
